Moodie description:
Moodie is an open-source and self-hostable mood tracker with a
                plethora of features that work with and for you. It’s currently
                being developed by 2 software engineering students for a school
                project, but we plan on making it a fully-featured application.
                It’s privacy-oriented, secure, and incredibly easy to use, but
                don’t trust us, just follow me.
